item.title: FTC Sues Ticket Resale Company, Alleging Eras Tour Price Gouging Scheme
item.description: The agency sued Maryland-based Key Investment Group, alleging that the company violated the BOTS Act to obtain thousands of Eras Tour tickets and resell them for millions of dollars.
